snippet.title: Amber Heard Was Arrested In 2009 For Domestic Violence Against Her Ex Girlfriend
snippet.description:
Amber Heard arrested for Domestic Violence with then-girlfriend Tasya van Ree Click here to read more: .

Court Hearing 14 Sept 2009 - Amber Heard Alleged Abuse Against Then Partner Tasy van Ree Amber Heard domestic violence arrest unearthed: Actress .

Amber Heard was once arrested for domestic violence against her ex partner, it has been reported.The actress has recently been granted a temporary retraining .
